Forbole [ˈfɔːbəl] is a well-established blockchain validator and developer since 2017. As of 31 Mar 2021, the value of digital assets staked with us was worth more than $1 billion.

We adopt a diversified and inclusive approach to build a cross-cultural team. Our teammates are currently located in Hong Kong 🥟, Italy 🍕, Taiwan 🍜, the UK 🫖 and Egypt 🥙 who speak 10 different languages. 

We are the developer and maintainer of the opensource Interchain block explorer [Big Dipper](https://bigdipper.live/). We believe every chain should have an easy-to-use explorer to reach their end users.

We are the developer of the decentralized social protocol [Desmos](https://desmos.network) which empowers the social profile you are reading right now 😏. Learn more about creating your own [Desmos Profile](https://bit.ly/2Y3cO0f).

content.description:
This governance proposal is to turn on the inflation described in the [Desmos Project Plan](https://www.desmos.network/files/desmos-project-plan-v0.4.2.pdf).
If this proposal is passed, annual inflation of `DSM` will be between 40% to 80% according to the level of staking ratio.
If you agree on this, please vote `YES`.
If you do not agree on this, please vote `NO`.
If you do not understand what this is, please vote `ABSTAIN`.
If you think this is a spam, please vote `NO WITH VETO`.
